My cousin got the Sinful 7 cake and I had to refrain from eating it all when she let me try it, my friend got the Rocky Road brownie which was also decadent and delicious, and my Berry Crème Brule was outstanding.
I am looking forward to the next time I'm out in Mesa so I can go here again.

